Monsters versus humans. An endless war.
A war that has spanned countless generations.
And then the cycle repeats itself
over and over and over again.
Just as humans reclaim their world, the monsters
decimate them and everything they have once more.
This cycle is set to repeat time and time again
until the Overworld itself is completely gone.
